description: Rock Tech Lithium Inc. engages in the exploration and development of lithium properties. It holds a 100% interest in the Georgia Lake lithium project comprising 277 claim units and 41 mining leases located in the Thunder Bay Mining District of Ontario. The company was formerly known as Rock Tech Resources Inc. and changed its name to Rock Tech Lithium Inc. in April 2010. Rock Tech Lithium Inc. was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
